      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable workhorse that gets the job done? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next chapter! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years of service, it remains a dependable choice for anyone seeking a practical and affordable ride. It\u2019s a great opportunity to own a functional vehicle that still has plenty of life left in it!",
