    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty car! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still running like a champ. It\u2019s been well-loved and looked after, so it's ready to hit the road for many more adventures with you. It\u2019s got that perfect balance of being super dependable while still looking great in the driveway. If you're looking for a solid ride that won't let you down, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the legendary S54 platform. The 3.2L inline-six delivers linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefitting from a recent VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, featuring documented rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to maintain factory-spec kinematics. While the car shows minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the individual throttle bodies offer immediate response, and the suspension dampening remains firm and controlled. A performance-oriented build ready for the spirited enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regular maintenance performed. Clean interior and exterior. Reliable performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
