    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2014 Porsche Cayman S that perfectly balances performance with daily usability. Finished in timeless Agate Grey Metallic, the paint holds a deep, brilliant shine, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with spirited weekend drives. The interior is a highlight\u2014the black leather sport seats are supple and free of bolster wear, the buttons show no peeling, and the cabin retains that signature Porsche smell, remaining strictly smoke-free. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. I have kept a comprehensive folder of all service receipts, including a major 40k-mile service recently completed. The 3.4L flat-six engine runs smoothly, and the PDK transmission shifts with crisp precision. It sits on a set of Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires with significant tread depth remaining. This is a turn-key, honest enthusiast car that is ready for the canyon roads today.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
