      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, an exemplary choice for the discerning driver who values both performance and reliability. This automobile has undergone a rigorous professional inspection to ensure its mechanical integrity and aesthetic standards are upheld. With a comprehensive service history and refined interior appointments, it offers a sophisticated driving experience. This represents an outstanding opportunity to acquire a well-preserved asset that balances luxury with proven durability.",
      "price": 36450.0,
